# Core

- **Source of truth:** `docs/ai/` for architecture; step-by-step detail in `docs/ai/skills/`. **Auto-selected workflows:** project Agent Skills under `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` (read the skill whose description matches the task).
- **Before coding:** locate the closest existing feature (same stack, same folder family). Copy its structure; do not invent layers or folders.
- **Scope:** smallest change that satisfies the request. No drive-by refactors, no new architecture unless an existing pattern already does it.
- **Finish:** run the real validation commands for every touched workspace (see `docs/ai/monorepo-overview.md`). Fix failures before stopping.
